Package gr.forth.ics.jbenchy.diagram

Provides core support for generating diagrams, typically from reports created by an Aggregator.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Diagram A diagram is a tabular data set, comprising a number of named dimensions (variables), and a value for each cell.
 

Class Summary
DiagramFactory A factory of diagrams, based on Aggregator reports.
DiagramFactory.DiagramImpl A diagram implementation.
 

Package gr.forth.ics.jbenchy.diagram Description

Provides core support for generating diagrams, typically from reports created by an Aggregator.

Package Specification

The data set that supports a diagram is abstracted by the Diagram interface.

See DiagramFactory for API to create Diagram instances from an Aggregator report. See subpackages for supported renderings of this abstraction to actual diagrams.
